Description: Enter a sequence of 0s and 1s to start the clock, and enter more sequences before it runs out, while trying not to be fooled by fake solves and strikes. Tags: clock, display, 2-digit-number, number, submit, reset, 0, 1, O, I, rusty, event-secret-santa-1
Name: Overclock

Souvenir.Explanation: Souvenir could ask about the values on the display before the clock was been started, or during the response section that the module solved after. Souvenir could also ask about any fake solves or strikes.
